 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Vyke's War Spear</strong>&nbsp;is a <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Great Spears" href="/Great+Spears" target="">Great Spear</a>&nbsp;in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. The <strong>Vyke's War Spear</strong>&nbsp;scales primarily with Dexterity, and Faith. It is a good weapon for those users with high <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Dexterity" href="/Dexterity" target="">Dexterity</a>&nbsp;builds and Faith / Dexterity Hybrid builds. Note players should use it wisely because its Ash of War inflicts madness on both their enemies and themselves.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>War spear singed and blistered by fingers, used by Vyke, Knight of the Roundtable Hold.</em></p> 
 <p><em>Like Vyke himself, it has been tormented by the yellow flame of frenzy from within.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to Find Vyke's War Spear in&nbsp;Elden Ring</h3> 
<p>The Vyke's War Spear weapon can be found at the following location:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Dropped&nbsp;by&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Festering Fingerprint Vyke" href="/Festering+Fingerprint+Vyke" target="">Festering Fingerprint Vyke</a>. [<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive map?id=6369&amp;lat=-115.609375&amp;lng=72.535609&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA" href="/Interactive+map?id=6369&amp;lat=-115.609375&amp;lng=72.535609&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA">Elden Ring Map here</a>]</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring Vyke's War Spear Notes &amp; Tips</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Weapon <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Skills" href="/Skills" target="">Skill</a>: <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Frenzyflame Thrust" href="/Frenzyflame+Thrust" target="">Frenzyflame Thrust</a></li> 
 <li>This weapon cannot be infused with <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Ashes of War" href="/Ashes+of+War" target="">Ashes of War</a></li> 
 <li><strong>Vyke's War Spear</strong> can be upgraded by using <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Somber Smithing Stones" href="/Somber+Smithing+Stones" target="">Somber Smithing Stones</a></li> 
 <li>Causes <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Madness" href="/Madness" target="">Madness</a> Buildup: <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Madness" href="/Madness"><img title="Causes Madness Buildup" src="/file/Elden-Ring/madness_status_effect_elden_ring_wiki_guide_100px.png" alt="madness status effect elden ring wiki guide 100px" width="18"> (65)</a></li> 
 <li>Sell Value:&nbsp;&nbsp;<img title="Runes" src="/file/Elden-Ring/er-runes-13.png" alt="er runes 13" width="18" height="18">&nbsp;500</li> 
 <li>Other notes and player tips go here</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Moveset &amp; Videos in&nbsp;Elden Ring for&nbsp;Vyke's War Spear</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Videos for the Vyke's War Spear Coming Soon</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Vyke's War Spear Upgrades in&nbsp;Elden Ring</h3> 
<p>Please see the&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Upgrades" href="/Upgrades" target="">Upgrades</a>&nbsp;page to understand the weapon bolstering process.</p> 
<p>Requires regular reinforcement with&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Somber Smithing Stones" href="/Somber+Smithing+Stones" target="">Somber Smithing Stones</a></p> 
<p>This weapon&nbsp;cannot be enchanted with&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Magic Spells" href="/Magic+Spells" target="">Magic</a>&nbsp;or boosted with&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Consumables" href="/Consumables" target="">Consumables</a>.</p> 
