on fextralife, turn on caps lock, and begin pounding away on your mechanical keyboard in the comments section. You write a paragraph about how this spear is broken and trash, putting every ounce of your rage into this box. You slam the enter key and take a deep breath, you have done your holy duty to tell others on the internet that a virtual spear is broken and overpowered. You stroke your neck beard confidently, and shout up from the basement to your mother that you&apos;re hungry after your vigilante work, and require pizza rolls and more mountain dew. The title of Elden Lord does not grant enough gratitude to these heros. Please, my fellow elden ring players, if you see a comment bashing this weapon, be sure to reply to that post and thank that war-scarred veteran for their service. The invasion may be over, but the frenzy-flame butthurt will never fade...</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16763119" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16763119" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">6</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>124</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>5</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16763119"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16763119" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"><